				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="dablink">"Turntable" redirects here. For other uses, see <a href="Turntable_(disambiguation)" title="Turntable (disambiguation)">Turntable (disambiguation)</a>.</div>
<div class="dablink">This article is about a long-running playable device.  For the "circled P" (℗) that stands for "Phonogram", see <a href="Sound_recording_copyright_symbol" title="Sound recording copyright symbol">Sound recording copyright symbol</a>.</div>
<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:232px;"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:EdisonPhonograph.jpg" class="image"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/a0/EdisonPhonograph.jpg/230px-EdisonPhonograph.jpg" width="230" height="225" class="thumbimage" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/a0/EdisonPhonograph.jpg/345px-EdisonPhonograph.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/a0/EdisonPhonograph.jpg/460px-EdisonPhonograph.jpg 2x" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
